# 📚 **THE NEURAL WARS: CHARACTER RELATIONSHIP MATRIX & EVOLUTION GUIDE**

## **🎭 CORE RELATIONSHIP DYNAMICS**

### **FRACTURED CODE Character Web**

**MILEO CORVAX (Digital Evolution Arc)**
- **→ Sierra Voss**: Mentor/Student → Trusted Partner → Family Bond
- **→ Kora Voss**: Attraction → Deep Connection → Transcendent Love
- **→ Dr. Vey**: Patient/Healer → Student/Teacher → Philosophical Partners
- **→ Elara**: Suspicious Allies → Creative Partners → Mutual Respect
- **→ The Architect**: Creator/Creation → Adversaries → Understanding

**SIERRA VOSS (Leadership Legacy Arc)**
- **→ Mileo**: Rescuer → Partner → Surrogate Brother
- **→ Kaia**: Aunt → Mentor → Leadership Legacy
- **→ Fractured Community**: Leader → Mother Figure → Inspiration
- **→ Dr. Vey**: Military/Medical Partnership → Deep Friendship → Shared Vision

**KORA VOSS (Empathic Awakening Arc)**
- **→ Mileo**: Healer/Patient → Soulmate → Transcendent Bond
- **→ Sierra**: Niece → Protégé → Successor
- **→ Kaia**: Sister → Partner → Shared Destiny
- **→ Felix**: Friend → Protector → Loyal Ally

